V3 Value SetActRelationshipFulfills

The source act fulfills (in whole or in part) the target act. Source act must be in a mood equal or more actual than the target act.

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include codes from http://terminology.hl7.org/CodeSystem/v3-ActRelationshipType where concept is-a FLFS
